features: 【3-Port 67W USB-C Fast Car Charger Cigarette Lighter】: Using highly efficient components + advanced chipset perfectly compatible with iPhone/SamSung device, Our 67W USB-C Car Charger Adapter can charging three iPhone 16 simultaneously. Using original USB-C terminal and 56Ω pull-up resistor adjust voltage & current output to match connected iPhone 16, Rombica's intelligent charging tech ever charges your iPhone 16 at its fastest possible, the charging speed is directly increased by 9 times.

【Leading the Way Dynamic Temperature Sensor】: Built-in intelligent power management chip and advanced temperature control system automatically match the current required by the iPhone 16, Adopt integrated superconductor material which engineered for reduced resistance, boosting charging efficiency. Features a Dynamic Temperature Sensor which actively monitors temperature, and a Power Tuner Chip which adjusts power output safeguard your connected iPhone 16/Galaxy/Pixel battery safety.

【MFi Certified Type-C Charge Braided Cable】: Rombica's Type-C Braided Cable Consists of E-Marker Chipset and Original USB-C Connector. Compatible with following devices: iPhone 16/16 Plus/16 Pro/16 Pro Max/15/15 Plus/15 Pro/15 Pro Max, iPad Pro 12.9 inch, iPad Pro 11 inch, iPad Air 5th/4th, iPad 10th, iPad Mini 6, AirPods, SamSung Galaxy/Note, Google Pixel, Moto and more. MFi Certified Type-C Cable comes with surge protection, overvoltage protection and automatic chip recognition functions.

【Exclusive All-new iActivePower Safety Charging Tech】: Certified by UL, ETL, FCC, CE, ROHS approve. Embedded Vehicle Smart Chipset can auto-detect iPhone connected in each port while also identifying the appropriate current to charge your device and make sure uninterrupted fast charging. Rombica's exclusive all-new iActivePower safety system with overload protection to enhanced safe charging, Provide continuous temperature monitoring and output control to protect iPhone 16/SamSung Galaxy device.

【Premium Materials and Design】: The housing made of Environmentally Friendly All Zinc Alloy + ABS Fireproof Materials offers better scratch resistance, heat dissipation, attractive design, and long service life, perfect for the most untouched vehicle interiors. Gold-plated tubing reduces heat during charging while maximizing charging efficiency. The blue ring LED indicator can help you to find the charge ports easily in the dark, Easily fits in a car Cigarette Lighter socket with limited space.
